<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَتْرابٌ قد استوين سنا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[سورة ص <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> : الآيات ٥٣ الى ٥٨]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هذا ما تُوعَدُونَ لِيَوْمِ الْحِسابِ <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> إِنَّ هذا لَرِزْقُنا ما لَهُ مِنْ نَفادٍ <span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> هذا وَإِنَّ لِلطَّاغِينَ لَشَرَّ مَآبٍ <span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> جَهَنَّمَ يَصْلَوْنَها فَبِئْسَ الْمِهادُ <span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> هذا فَلْيَذُوقُوهُ حَمِيمٌ وَغَسَّاقٌ <span class="c2">(٥٧)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَآخَرُ مِنْ شَكْلِهِ أَزْواجٌ <span class="c2">(٥٨)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٥٣-<span class="c5"> هذا ما تُوعَدُونَ لِيَوْمِ الْحِسابِ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هذا النعيم.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لِيَوْمِ الْحِسابِ ليوم القيامة.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٥٤-<span class="c5"> إِنَّ هذا لَرِزْقُنا ما لَهُ مِنْ نَفادٍ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لَرِزْقُنا لعطاؤنا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>نَفادٍ نهاية.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٥٥-<span class="c5"> هذا وَإِنَّ لِلطَّاغِينَ لَشَرَّ مَآبٍ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هذا أي هذا النعيم جزاؤنا للمتقين.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَإِنَّ لِلطَّاغِينَ المتمردين.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مَآبٍ مآل ومنقلب.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥٦-<span class="c5"> جَهَنَّمَ يَصْلَوْنَها فَبِئْسَ الْمِهادُ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>يَصْلَوْنَها يقاسون حرها.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>الْمِهادُ الفراش.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٥٧-<span class="c5"> هذا فَلْيَذُوقُوهُ حَمِيمٌ وَغَسَّاقٌ:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>هذا ماء.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَلْيَذُوقُوهُ يؤمرون أن يذوقوه.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>حَمِيمٌ بلغ الغاية فى الحرارة.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَغَسَّاقٌ وصديد أهل النار.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٥٨-<span class="c5"> وَآخَرُ مِنْ شَكْلِهِ أَزْواجٌ:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَآخَرُ وعذاب آخر.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>مِنْ شَكْلِهِ من شكل هذا العذاب.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>أَزْواجٌ أنواع مزدوجة.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>